Interface ProgrammaticDriverConfigLoaderBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OngoingConfigOptions<ProgrammaticDriverConfigLoaderBuilder>

    public interface ProgrammaticDriverConfigLoaderBuilder
extends OngoingConfigOptions<ProgrammaticDriverConfigLoaderBuilder>
    A builder that allows the creation of a config loader where options are overridden programmatically.
